<p>That is a great question Steve!</p>
<p>I know I only get Internet service.  No landline telephone, no cable,or any of the other services.</p>
<p>As with our privacy I suppose we have to determine the level of compromise we are willing to make.  Sure, I could be completely private living in the Amazon but that is not really the lifestyle for me.  But I think you understand the principle of becoming aware of how much you are feeding the parasitic vampire squids and cutting back where possible.</p>
</div>
					</dd>
